 4ï¸âƒ£ What is URL (Uniform Resource Locator)

â†’ URL ek web address hota hai jo resource ka location batata hai

â†’ Example
[http://3.110.25.10](http://3.110.25.10)
[https://mywebsite.com](https://mywebsite.com)

â†’ Parts of URL
Protocol â†’ http / https
Domain / IP â†’ server address
Path â†’ file ka location (index.html)

